OL,6,FA care home manager who sexually
OL,7,Fassaulted 'vulnerable' patients and
OL,8,Ffellow staff has been jailed.
OL,10,FWilliam Malcolm, known as Bill, was
OL,11,Ffound guilty of ten counts of sexual
OL,12,Fassault, two of ill treatment of a
OL,13,Fperson in care and one of racially
OL,14,Faggravated harassment at a trial at
OL,15,FNewcastle Crown Court in March 2025.
