OL,3,CCare home manager who sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted 'vulnerable' patients jailed
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old, from South Shields,
OL,7,Fwas a registered mental health nurse,
OL,8,Fcaring for vulnerable people with
OL,9,Fcomplex needs. The name of the
OL,10,Ffacility has not been released to
OL,11,Fprotect the identities of his victims.
OL,13,FDuring his trial, the court heard how
OL,14,FMalcolm used abusive language towards
OL,15,Fthose under his care, simulated sex,
OL,16,Fgroped and kissed them.
