OL,4,Cassaulted 'vulnerable' patients jailed
OL,6,FThe court was also told how he used
OL,7,Fracist and homophobic language and
OL,8,Frepeatedly kissed and cuddled two
OL,9,Fvulnerable patients. One former
OL,10,Fcolleague describing his behaviour as
OL,11,F"disgusting".
OL,13,FVictim impact statements were also
OL,14,Fread out from some of the staff who
OL,15,Fworked alongside Malcolm detailing the
OL,16,Fsexual assaults and harassment they
OL,17,Ffaced on a regular basis.
